snippet.title: Magazine Editor - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Magazine Editor on: http://store.steampowered.com/app/596170/

You've got 9 weeks to prove your worth and get back to the rich, lucky and fun life. Your team consists of talented journalists with lots of ideas, but don't forget about the investors who're dictating the rules. Become the Chief Editor for this magazine and win the “Magazine of the Year” competition!

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
